  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM1.6.3">
<l>īṭu meṭuppumi līcaṉ</l>
<l>māṭu viṭāteṉ maṉaṉē</l>
<l>pāṭumeṉ ṉāvalaṉ pāṭa</l>
<l>lāṭume ṉaṅkama ṇaṅkē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Without any application or plan, the lord’s</l>
<l>place my mind does not let go of;</l>
<l>my tongue sing songs for him;</l>
<l>my body dances [like] a demon.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
